OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning mist patches and any
OL,6,Flow cloud quickly clearing. A warm day
OL,7,Fahead, with light winds and plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine. The sunshine may turn hazy
OL,9,Fat times, especially during the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening, then a clear
OL,13,Fnight for most. Some low cloud, mist
OL,14,Fand fog patches may develop as the
OL,15,Fnight progresses. Winds remaining
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
