OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAny low cloud and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a sunny day for all,
OL,7,Fwith light winds. Feeling very warm as
OL,8,Ftemperatures rise well above the
OL,9,Fseasonal average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FHigh
OL,12,Fpressure will keep it dry and settled,
OL,13,Fwith plenty of warm sunshine and winds
OL,14,Fremaining light. Some overnight fog
OL,15,Fpatches possible, mainly in the
OL,16,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
